name: Glow In The Dark Paint "Sampler"
description:
***$60 VALUE***


- Each order comes with additional instructions on how to apply and optimize your results

- Red GITD, Blue GITD, Green GITD, Violet GITD

- Water Resistant

- EASY to apply and requires NO prior knowledge or expertise

- Can be applied with an airbrush or paintbrush

- Scuff Proof

- Dries Clear (Except the Red which dries Infrared)

- Premixed with a resilient sealant so it is very adhesive and locks in the glow

- Works best from a full 15 minute charge from sunlight

- Immediately emits glow in the smallest absence of light after a charge

- Reaction takes place under chemiluminescence using the best phosphorescence materials available to give the greatest emission of light

How long will the paint last?

- The paint will continue to glow through chemiluminescence for the shoes entire lifespan

What Size Should I Buy?

- 7.39mL: Trim outsole and do fine details of a shoe

- 14.78mL: Paint the entire sole (under & sides) & do fine details

- 22.17mL: Paint the entire sole (under & sides) & do larger details

- 29.56mL: Paint multiple soles (under & sides) & do small details

- 36.59mL: Paint multiple soles entirely (under & sides) and do fine details

(Be mindful if you have larger size shoe to paint you may want to get a larger quantity of paint to be safe)

**CONTENTS ARE VERY CONCENTRATED SO A LITTLE GOES A LONG WAY. **
